    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニピの全国ツアー開始前のある日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ファンレターがこんなに沢山……！\nどれから読もうかな……",
      "startTime": 5.8000000954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "全国ツアーに合わせて、ファンの願いを叶えて回る\nサプライズ企画をやるんだったよな",
      "startTime": 11.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ファンレターは逃げないから\n気になったものからじっくり読めばいいさ",
      "startTime": 15.9401240017,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3359.8759983000014,
          "startTime": 19.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、この可愛い便せんのものから……\nふむふむ……え……？",
      "startTime": 23.4767125924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どうした？\n何か変なことでも書いてあったか？",
      "startTime": 27.8000008901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、そんなことないです！\nただ、ちょっとびっくりしちゃって……",
      "startTime": 33.4713627974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "私に憧れてダンスを始めた子からで\n大会に向けて練習しているらしいんです",
      "startTime": 41.0046976566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "それで、憧れの私にいつかダンスを\n習ってみたいと書いてあって……",
      "startTime": 48.5046979109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんの方がダンスは得意なのに\nどうして私なんだろう……？",
      "startTime": 55.0713645775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "千紗のダンスに心を打たれたんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 57.8713643233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？\nそんなこと……あり得るんでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 62.0232011158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "私はダンスが特別上手な訳じゃないし\nむしろみんなに追いつくのにいつも必死です",
      "startTime": 71.1232011158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "なのに、この子は私を選んでくれました\nその理由がどうしても気になって……",
      "startTime": 79.5565344492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "とりあえず、頼みを聞いてみてから\n考えるっていうのはどうだ？",
      "startTime": 85.5000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "どうして選んでくれたのかも\nその時に聞けばいいと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 89.2333360036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……\n悩むよりは行動あるのみ、ですよね！",
      "startTime": 93.4016590118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "私、やってみます！",
      "startTime": 97.5683193207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、誰かにダンスを教えたことなんて\n一度もないので……",
      "startTime": 103.7016513824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、まずは俺で練習してみたらどうだ？\nダンス未経験者だから、うってつけだぞ",
      "startTime": 109.4666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "い、いいんですか！？\n嫌じゃなかったら、ぜひお願いしたいです！",
      "startTime": 115.1041294415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、よろしくお願いしますね\nって、あれ……そのジャージ、どうしたんですか？",
      "startTime": 124.2374643008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "上も下も、七分丈というか、六分丈というか……\n随分キツそうですけど……",
      "startTime": 135.5707976341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あー……いや、動きやすい格好ってこれしかなくてな\n中学の時のだから、サイズもギリギリで……",
      "startTime": 143.8000031789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "本当だ、名札が縫い付けてある……\nも、物持ちがいいんですね、とってもエコです……！",
      "startTime": 150.9241806031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "無理にフォローしなくていいからな！？\nまぁ、とりあえず始めようか",
      "startTime": 157.2333405813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　では、まずは私がお手本を見せるので\n同じように踊ってみて下さい",
      "startTime": 164.4330662093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "こんな感じです。では、真似してみて下さい",
      "startTime": 172.8664043746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "こうで……よっ、ととと……！？　はっ！　ほおっ！？\nは、はいー！　っと……こ、こんな感じか？",
      "startTime": 183.0666718801,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6319.772847700023,
          "startTime": 189.3864447278
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "初めてだと、なかなか難しいですよね\nでも、しっかり最後までやりきって凄いと思います",
      "startTime": 195.5531113944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "わ、我ながら、かなり不格好だったと思うが\n千紗は優しいなぁ……",
      "startTime": 204.5333385468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "では、改めて最初から……あ、そう、そこなんですけど\nちょっと失礼しますね",
      "startTime": 213.3985308332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、腕をもっと……こう\n大きく上げた方が見栄えも良くなると思います",
      "startTime": 219.8318641665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "って……あれ？　{user}さん？\nどうして固まっちゃったんですか……？",
      "startTime": 228.0651974998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや……ファンを相手にするなら\nあまり体を密着させない方がいいと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 233.9333385468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs023.m4a",
